<h1>The Drone Papers</h1>
<p><span>The Intercept has obtained a cache of secret documents 
detailing the inner workings of the U.S. military’s assassination 
program in Afghanistan, Yemen, and Somalia. The documents, provided by a
 whistleblower, offer an unprecedented glimpse into Obama’s drone wars.</span></p>
<p class="rm-manual">Illustration by The Intercept</p>
